-- CIG Pannonia Drops to Record Low as Quarterly Loss Widens 76%
-- B y   A n d r a s   G e r g e l y
-- 2012-05-21T09:14:45Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-21/cig-pannonia-drops-to-record-low-as-quarterly-loss-widens-76-.html
CIG Pannonia Eletbiztosito Nyrt., a
Hungarian life insurer, fell to a record low after reporting
that its  net loss  widened 76 percent in the first quarter.  The shares fell 10 percent to 305 forint by 10:58 a.m. in
Budapest, the lowest since its listing in November 2010.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andras Gergely in Budapest at 
 agergely@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
